## Enforcement

If you find yourself about to create ANY UI element:

1. **STOP** - Check if shadcn/ui has a component for this
2. **SEARCH** - Look at [shadcn/ui documentation](https://ui.shadcn.com)
3. **INSTALL** - Run `npx shadcn@latest add [component-name]`
4. **USE** - Import and use the shadcn/ui component

**NEVER CREATE CUSTOM UI. ALWAYS USE SHADCN/UI.**
